@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qavvbh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.94 / v0) / wp.exp(0.85))
    tmp = 0.37
    tmp = 0.99
    v1 = (0.51 / v1)
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.59 + v0 + 0.51)) + wp.abs(0.55))
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.26 / v0 + 0.59)) - ((v2 + 0.60 * v2 + 0.22) + (v1 + 0.66 * v2 + 0.64)))
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
